item.title: Slater
item.description: Short Bio “Slater! The pyromaniac Fire Chief he thrives in the chaos of Los Santos. He likes things that move fast, go boom or fly high (well preferably all 3 at once). And Would burn down the city to protect those he cares about!” Assositations San Andreas Fire Rescue | Chief Prometheus Heavy Industries - See Also Catfe, Slaters Supers | CEO / Owner San Andreas Police - See Also LSPD | Pilot, Pilot Training, Tactical Medic, Annoyance
